  "title": "Chef",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>· Set up workstations with all needed ingredients and cooking equipment</p><p>· Prepare ingredients to use in cooking (chopping and peeling vegetables, cutting meat etc.)</p><p>· Cook food in various utensils or grillers</p><p>· Check food while cooking to stir or turn</p><p>· Ensure great presentation by dressing dishes before they are served</p><p>· Keep a sanitized and orderly environment in the kitchen</p><p>· Ensure all food and other items are stored properly</p><p>· Check quality of ingredients</p><p>· Monitor stock and place orders when there are shortages</p><p><strong>Requirements and skills</strong></p><p>· Proven experience as chef</p><p>· Experience in using cutting tools, cookware and bakeware</p><p>· Knowledge of various cooking procedures and methods (grilling, baking, boiling etc.)</p><p>· Ability to follow all sanitation procedures</p><p>· Ability to work in a team</p><p>· Very good communication skills</p><p>· Excellent physical condition and stamina</p><p>· Able to work night shift and public holiday</p>",
